history.proof: intros xs k H. induction xs as [|x xs IH]. - simpl in H. contradiction. - simpl in H. destruct x. + simpl. destruct H. * left. injection H. intros. subst. reflexivity. * right. apply IH. auto. + apply IH. hauto lq: on depth: 3. + apply IH. hauto lq: on depth: 3.
